From Ancient Athens these creatures burst forth into the Modern World.
Young Athenian captives were sacrificed to these creatures within their
homes of the legendary labyrinthes. The Greek Hero Theseus killed the
last of these horrible monsters centuries ago, but Kindred got bored one day
and brought them back. Now they feast upon the noble (and not-so-noble)
inhabitants of this land.
 
Favored Class: Warrior

Natural Ability: Charge

*************************************
~

0 PIXIE~
These playful, fairy-like elfen creatures of unknown origin are mischievous
to the extreme. These mythical beings are very real indeed, and are known
far and wide for their speed and agility. Close cousins to the brownies,
they tend to inhabit secluded woodland areas far from civilization.

Favored Class: Mage

Natural Ability: Pixie Dust

*************************************
