0 GARGOYLE~
These blotches of hideosity that roam freely over the land are said to be
the fabled and hideous spawn of Medusa .  With the skin of an aborted fetus,
these monstrosities scavage over the land with frightening abandon, smashing
everything in their path while fending off blows with their stoney skin.  
 
