0 CENTAUR~
Descended from Ixion, the savage followers of Dionysus, half-man
half-horse, the Centaur have traveled down through the ages, sounding the
trumpets of revolution.  Known for their grace and agility in combat, and
the fluidity of both their music and their tongue, they comprise some of the
greatest of the Human scholars of any age.  Not to mention a most devasting
KICK !  

Favored Class: Warrior

Natural Ability: Double Kick

*************************************
