0 ORC~
These foul creatures were created by Morgoth in the Great Darkness during
the first age of Middle-earth.  Through dark sorcery, the Great Enemy
corrupted elves and transformed them into these brutish slaves.  Orcs
delight only in watching things suffer and die.  These soulless creatures
bear special malice to elves and dwarves, against whom they have fought many
battles.  Be wary for Orcs are tough in combat and no one person should ever
take a battle with an Orc lightly. 

Favored Class: Berserker, shaman

Natural Ability: War Chant

*************************************
